data.description: Welcome to River's Bend at Pecan Park, a beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home with an office on 1/4 acre of land! This luxurious home features an open floor plan and boasts of plenty of amenities. The kitchen includes granite countertops, subway tile backsplash and abundant cabinet space for all your cooking needs. Retreat to the owner's suite featuring a custom closet system for optimal storage solutions. Step outside and enjoy the lushly landscaped front yard or relax in the backyard under the covered patio. Living in River's Bend at Pecan Park is even more special with access to the Colorado river, community pool and several hiking/biking trails nearby! Make this stunning home yours today!
